				<h1 class=3D"entry-title">Area of an Ellipse</h1>
			</header>
		=09
					=09
			<div class=3D"entry-content">
				<div class=3D"entry themeform">
				=09
<div class=3D"wp-block-image"><figure class=3D"alignright"><img decoding=3D=
